---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact
description: Contact Forgotten Industries.
permalink: /contact.html
canonical: https://forgotten-industries.net/contact.html
---
<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner masthead-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Inbound signal</p>
      <h1>Contact</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Use the domain address for restoration notes, CaseLabs history, inventory inquiries, source corrections, and documentation work.</p>
    </div>
    <img class="hero-image" src="/assets/forgotten-industries.jpeg" alt="Forgotten Industries logo, EST MMXIV">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mirror-band" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Project address</p>
      <h2 id="contact-heading">One clean point of contact.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dl class="ledger">
        <div>
          <dt>Primary</dt>
          <dd><a href="mailto:{{ site.contact }}" data-track="contact-email">{{ site.contact }}</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Archive</dt>
          <dd><a href="mailto:{{ site.archiveContact }}" data-track="contact-archive">{{ site.archiveContact }}</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Field Notes</dt>
          <dd><a href="{{ site.fieldNotesSubscribeUrl }}" data-track="subscribe-field-notes">{{ site.fieldNotesContact }}</a></dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band" aria-labelledby="subjects-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Useful subjects</p>
      <h2 id="subjects-heading">Send evidence, context, and corrections.</h2>
    </div>
    <ul class="shelf-list">
      <li>
        <h3>Restoration Notes</h3>
        <p>Part identification, compatibility notes, repair references, and measurements.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>CaseLabs History</h3>
        <p>Old orders, accessories, provenance, build logs, and hardware context.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Inventory Inquiry</h3>
        <p>Questions about archive records, condition, disposition, or missing details.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Writing Or Documentation</h3>
        <p>Corrections, source links, interviews, and project collaboration.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="external-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">External routes</p>
      <h2 id="external-heading">Archive adjacent, not archive replacing.</h2>
    </div>
    <ul class="link-list">
      <li>
        <h3><a href="{{ site.githubUrl }}" data-track="outbound-github">GitHub</a></h3>
        <p>Repository source, generated archive data, and project structure.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="{{ site.eleventyUrl }}" data-track="outbound-eleventy">Eleventy</a></h3>
        <p>Static site generator that builds this archive.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
